d":"comes","count":1},{"word":"anyway","count":1},{"word":"stop","count":1},{"word":"disbanding","count":1},{"word":"made","count":1},{"word":"picks","count":1},{"word":"members","count":1},{"word":"duel","count":1},{"word":"last","count":1},{"word":"standing","count":1},{"word":"shot","count":1},{"word":"taking","count":1},{"word":"defeated","count":1},{"word":"faculty's","count":1},{"word":"disbandment","count":1},{"word":"request","count":1},{"word":"approved","count":1},{"word":"loses","count":1},{"word":"lose","count":1},{"word":"beat","count":1},{"word":"paperwork","count":1},{"word":"goes","count":1},{"word":"bye-bye","count":1},{"word":"drop","count":1},{"word":"whole","count":1},{"word":"thing","count":1},{"word":"problem","count":1},{"word":"crazy","count":1},{"word":"especially","count":1},{"word":"far","count":1},{"word":"nobody","count":1},{"word":"close","count":1},{"word":"beating","count":1},{"word":"met","count":1},{"word":"match","count":1},{"word":"earlier","count":1},{"word":"proved","count":1},{"word":"hunch","count":1},{"word":"defeat","count":1},{"word":"save","count":1},{"word":"swinging","count":1},{"word":"dennis","count":1},{"word":"responsible","count":1},{"word":"managing","count":1},{"word":"campus","count":1},{"word":"discipline","count":1},{"word":"total","count":1},{"word":"hard-ass","count":1},{"word":"plays","count":1},{"word":"everything","count":1},{"word":"book","count":1},{"word":"weird","count":1},{"word":"seem","count":1},{"word":"rules","count":1},{"word":"axe","count":1},{"word":"grind","count":1},{"word":"definitely","count":1},{"word":"accept","count":1},{"word":"thank","count":1},{"word":"said","count":1},{"word":"knew","count":1},{"word":"someone","count":1},{"word":"threw","count":1},{"word":"away","count":1},{"word":"ahem","count":1},{"word":"understand","count":1},{"word":"dear","count":1},{"word":"friend","count":1},{"word":"rival","count":1},{"word":"mentioned","count":1},{"word":"sec","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"interview","count":1},{"word":"gave","count":1},{"word":"exactly","count":1},{"word":"happened","count":1},{"word":"looked","count":1},{"word":"clear","count":1},{"word":"dedication","count":1},{"word":"work","count":1},{"word":"put","count":1},{"word":"lot","count":1},{"word":"pressure","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"working","count":1},{"word":"secret","count":1},{"word":"showed","count":1},{"word":"impressive","count":1},{"word":"skills","count":1},{"word":"speak","count":1},{"word":"manager","count":1},{"word":"grant","count":1},{"word":"qualification","count":1},{"word":"participate","count":1},{"word":"lahai-roi","count":1},{"word":"ranked","count":1},{"word":"unlike","count":1},{"word":"single-elimination","count":1},{"word":"apex","count":1},{"word":"championship","count":1},{"word":"held","count":1},{"word":"divisions","count":1},{"word":"follow","count":1},{"word":"points-based","count":1},{"word":"system","count":1},{"word":"qualified","count":1},{"word":"duelists","count":1},{"word":"roster","count":1},{"word":"earn","count":1},{"word":"points","count":1},{"word":"season","count":1},{"word":"ends","count":1},{"word":"highest","count":1},{"word":"score","count":1},{"word":"crowned","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"already","count":1},{"word":"sent","count":1},{"word":"coordinates","count":1},{"word":"competitors","count":1},{"word":"terminal","count":1},{"word":"feel","count":1},{"word":"free","count":1},{"word":"anytime","count":1},{"word":"luck","count":1},{"word":"looking","count":1},{"word":"forward","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"become","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"—Game. So, what do you think, Ashild?","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"Oh, just a minor administrative hiccup, that's all. A few professors have some... well, mild opinions about us. Long story short, they want me to disband the fan club.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"Actually, it's really just Professor Calith who wants the club gone. The others probably have their own reasons, but they all ended up on the same side.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"Ever since he returned from a trip to Septimont, he's convinced that playing Peaks of Prestige is a bad idea. Thinks we're all going to start flunking because we're too obsessed with dueling.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"...In reality, we have a rule in our fan club: If your grades slip because you're spending too much time dueling, you'll be kicked out.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"But don't worry. We've never actually had to kick anyone out. Everyone here gets that school comes first.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"Anyway, to stop the professors from disbanding the club, I made a bet with them.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"I'm the \"leader\" for the club, and Calith is the \"leader\" for the professors. Each side picks members to duel, and the last two standing get a shot at taking us down.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"If a leader gets defeated before the faculty's disbandment request is approved, that side loses the bet.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"If we lose, or we can't beat them before the paperwork goes through... we can say bye-bye to dueling.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"But if we win, the professors have to back off and drop the whole thing.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"The problem is, all the professors are crazy good, especially Professor Calith. So far, nobody in the club has even come close to beating him.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"But then I met you... And that match earlier proved my hunch was right. You're the one who can defeat the professors and save our club.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"If you want to come out swinging, start with Professor Dennis.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"He's responsible for managing campus discipline. Total hard-ass, plays everything by the book.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"What's weird is that it doesn't seem like he's against Peaks of Prestige because it's \"against the rules.\" He's got some other axe to grind.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"He'll definitely accept your challenge. Go get us that first win!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"Thank you, {PlayerName}.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700008},{"text":"Right, Professor Calith, you said you knew someone who threw it all away for this game...?","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Ahem... I think I understand now. So <i>you're</i> that \"dear friend and rival\" Furius has mentioned before...","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Just a sec, let me find that interview Furius gave in Septimont...","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"I don't know what exactly happened between you two... But I don't think Furius ever looked down on you.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"It's clear that your dedication and hard work put a lot of pressure on him. He must have been working hard in secret too... He just never showed it.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"...Impressive. Your skills speak for themselves, {PlayerName}.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Now, as division manager, I grant you the qualification to participate in the Lahai-Roi division Ranked Tournament.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Unlike the single-elimination \"Apex Duelist Championship\" held in Septimont, our divisions follow a points-based system.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Qualified duelists can challenge anyone on the tournament roster. Win, and you earn points.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"When the season ends, the duelist with the highest score will be crowned the Division Champion.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"I've already sent the coordinates of the other competitors to your Terminal. Feel free to challenge them anytime.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Good luck, {PlayerName}! I'm looking forward to the day you become our Division Champion.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019}]}